ia.org/resource/Zain_Retherford\"}, {\"begin\": 195, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997330633, \"rank\": 2.669653909817553e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With Retherford's Olympic quota, the entire men's freestyle team has qualified for the 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 254, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's freestyle team has all six going, as well.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Retherford had to make the Olympic team in the most difficult way possible.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 412, \"end\": 422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With his back against the wall on Sunday, he posted four straight wins in less than three hours.\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Retherford's first match was the one with the least amount of drama.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 592, \"end\": 602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Retherford started his scoring barrage with a head pinch attempt from his feet which gave him four points; however, the American fans collectively held their breath for a few seconds as Retherford was in danger of giving up a fall for a few seconds.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 661, \"end\": 671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}, {\"begin\": 781, \"end\": 789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.6273576169343454, \"rank\": 0.5937038668849354, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 847, \"end\": 857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Later in the opening period, Retherford ducked under a takedown attempt from Alibeg Alibegov (Bahrain) to extend his lead to 6-2.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 940, \"end\": 950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His punishing leg ride accounted for a couple of sets of exposure points, capped off by a fall.\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Retherford's second match was a 5-2 win over Abdulmazhid Kudeiv (Tajikistan).\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1138, \"end\": 1148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}, {\"begin\": 1203, \"end\": 1213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tajikistan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9996503995681212, \"rank\": 0.0003497212499487001, \"text\": \"Tajikistan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tajikistan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tajikistan_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former Penn State star got on the scoreboard quickly with a single leg he walked out of bounds for a step-out point.\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1227, \"end\": 1237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"score\": 0.9999521950902838, \"rank\": 4.667015252062396e-05, \"text\": \"Penn State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With time expiring in the first period, Retherford stayed on the offensive and claimed a takedown to take a 3-0 lead at the break.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Retherford iced the match with another takedown via the double leg early in the second period.\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1469, \"end\": 1479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the closing seconds, Kudiev got a takedown, but it wasn't enough.\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Up next for Retherford was India's Sujeet Kalkal.\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1646, \"end\": 1656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}, {\"begin\": 1661, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9999007186699438, \"rank\": 7.516191334544629e-05, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As you navigated through potential repechage matches, Kalkal appeared to be the most difficult matchup for Retherford.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1791, \"end\": 1801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like Retherford, Kalkal lost to Tulga Tumur Ochir (Mongolia) by a five-point margin.\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1808, \"end\": 1818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}, {\"begin\": 1835, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tulga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tulga\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tulga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tulga\"}, {\"begin\": 1854, \"end\": 1862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9996329525350518, \"rank\": 0.000367182179213317, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As expected, the Kakal matchup was the most challenging for Retherford.\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1949, \"end\": 1959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two-time Hodge Trophy winner appeared to be on his way to a takedown in the opening stanza; however, Kalkal worked his magic to reverse the favor and got a takedown of his own.\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It accounted for the only scoring of the first period.\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Retherford struck with a takedown of his own when he threw by a Kalkal attempt.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That put him ahead on criteria, though the scoreboard showed the pair knotted at two points a piece.\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Retherford was able to play defense for the last 1:43 of the match and got his hand raised.\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2379, \"end\": 2389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The win gave him a bronze medal, but it wasn't what Retherford was worried about.\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2523, \"end\": 2533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999150713883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He'd